snippet.title: Small Soldiers PS1 Intro
snippet.description: The Intro to Small Soldiers for PS1. This isn't the best game otu there, and when I saw this broguht home to me as a tennager, I thought it would be pure crap. But Suprisingly, this game isn't crap. It's actualy a pretty decent game if you can get Past Archer's horrid running animation (He Runs like he just had a colon checkup ^^0)
